Hello! Thank you for calling GreenView Gas Solutions. My name is Sarah. Could I have your name, please?

Hi Sarah, my name is John.

Great to meet you, John! How can I assist you with your billing today?

I received a bill that seems a bit higher than usual, and I wanted to get some details about the charges.

I can definitely help with that. Could you please provide me with your account number so I can pull up your details?

Sure, it's five six seven eight nine three two one.

Thank you, John. I see your account now. Can I also confirm the last four digits of your registered phone number for security purposes?

Yes, it's four three two one.

Perfect, thank you. It looks like there was a recent change in rates on your account. I'll email you a detailed breakdown of your charges. Is there anything else I can help you with?

No, that's all I needed. Thank you for your help, Sarah.

You're welcome, John. Thank you for calling GreenView Gas Solutions. Have a great day!
